videos.headline: Demetris Robertson splits Gamecocks' D for TD
videos.description: Auburn strikes first behind Demetris Robertson's 10-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Demetris Robertson splits Gamecocks' D for TD) 2021/11/21 ESHEET

videos.headline: Auburn WR hits defender with nasty juke for 28-yard catch
videos.description: Shedrick Jackson makes the catch and jukes a South Carolina defender to get the first down for Auburn.

videos.headline: South Carolina's 4th-down gamble pays off with 28-yard TD
